high_descs: Turn to your right and walk until you get to the round table.
Pick up the tomato from in front of the bowl on the table.
Turn to your left and walk across the kitchen until you get to the stove.
Place the tomato in the microwave, warm it, then take it out again.
Turn around and walk back to the round table.
Place the tomato on the front right side of the table, between the ends of the two spoons.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed tomato on a table.

high_descs: turn around and go to your right to the white table
pick up a tomato from the table
turn around and carry the tomato to the stove on the opposite side of the room
put the tomato in the microwave that is above the stove, cook it, remove the cooked tomato
turn around and go back to the opposite side of the room back to the white table
put the cooked tomato on the table at the handle end of the two spoons
anns.task_desc: put a cooked tomato on the white table

high_descs: Turn right and walk until you clear the counter to your right then turn right and walk until you're even with the table on your left and then turn left when you get there and walk to the white table.
Pick up the tomato that's under the small bowl.

Turn left and walk until you're clear of the counter to your left then turn left when you get past it and walk until you're a few feet from the fridge then turn left and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the stove top.
Put the tomato in the microwave and cook it and then get it back out and close the door.
Walk back to where you got the tomato and take a half step right.
Put the tomato where the two ice cream scoops meet.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato on the table.
